<item>
            <title>[HBASE-8554] Scan should seek to startRow within a region</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8554</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently Scan.startRow() is only used for determining which Region to look up the row into but we do not seek within the region to the start row. Since its not uncommon to run with large sized regions these days 5G, this is suboptimal.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12647804">HBASE-8554</key>
            <summary>Scan should seek to startRow within a region</summary>
